  <titles>
    <title type="short" as="introduced">Employer Reversion Moratorium Act of 1988</title>
    <title type="official" as="introduced">A bill to amend title I of the Employee Retirement Income Security Act of 1974 to provide for a moratorium on reversions to employers of assets of terminated pension plans and to establish as a fiduciary duty that assets of such plans which would otherwise revert to the employer but for the moratorium must be maintained in trust until the end of the moratorium.</title>
